title: Jimi Hendrix Experience - Are You Experienced And More (2004) FL
description:
Disc One of this very fine bootleg follows the original 1967 UK release - with one exception: Track 1-3 is the official American Smash Hits version of "Red House". Track 2-3 is the version that was included in the original UK version of "Are You Experienced". Disc Two includes different versions from the original studio sessions.
